title: Quest Hunter v0.9.32s
description: Welcome to the Dark World. The world that is ruled by its own laws. The world where fire is the main treasure, and a shovel is a loyal friend and assistant. There enough trouble for villains here but there's double trouble for heroes. As a hero you will have to: Level up and equip yourself. Claim some space for your camp from the Dark World.
